Package: Ternary
Version: 0.1.1.9001
Date: 2017-11-27
Title: Plot Ternary Diagrams
Description: Plots ternary diagrams using the standard graphics functions.  
  An alternative to 'ggtern', which uses the 'ggplot2' family of plotting functions.
